name: YYAI Token
description:
YYAI Token (YYAI33) is a Solana-based SPL token designed for testing and demonstration of tokenized asset infrastructure.
The token is part of the Stocks33 / xStocks experimental ecosystem, focusing on on-chain liquidity, wallet compatibility, and DEX integration on Solana.
YYAI33 is not a security, not an investment product, and does not represent equity, ownership, or profit rights. It is intended solely for technical testing, educational use, and ecosystem validation.
